Name: Total Profit Row Context
Expression:
SUMX(
 FactTransactions, -- Iterate rows (row context)
 FactTransactions[Revenue] - FactTransactions[CostOfGoods]
)

Name: Gross Profit
Expression:
VAR Revenue = SUM(FactTransactions[Revenue])
VAR Cost = SUM(FactTransactions[CostOfGoods])
RETURN Revenue - Cost

Name: -- Revenue % of Grand TotalRevenue % of Total
Expression:
DIVIDE(
    [Total Revenue],
    CALCULATE(
        [Total Revenue],
        ALL(DimProduct) -- Remove product filter
    )
)

Name: Performance Status
Expression:
IF(
    [Gross Margin %] >= 0.35, "Excellent",
    IF([Gross Margin %] >= 0.30, "Good",
    IF([Gross Margin %] >= 0.25, "Fair",
    "Poor"
)))

Name: Revenue % of Category
Expression:
VAR CategoryTotal = CALCULATE(
    [Total Revenue],
    ALLEXCEPT(DimProduct, DimProduct[Category])
)
RETURN DIVIDE([Total Revenue], CategoryTotal)

Name: Revenue % (ALL)
Expression:
DIVIDE(
    [Total Revenue],
    CALCULATE(
        [Total Revenue],
        ALL ( DimProduct )
    )
)

Name: Revenue % (ALLEXCEPT)
Expression:
VAR CategoryTotal =
    CALCULATE(
        [Total Revenue],
        ALLEXCEPT (
            DimProduct,
            DimProduct[Category]
        )
    )
RETURN
    DIVIDE ( [Total Revenue], CategoryTotal )

Name: Revenue % (ALLSELECTED)
Expression:
DIVIDE(
    [Total Revenue],
    CALCULATE(
        [Total Revenue],
        ALLSELECTED ( DimProduct )
    )
)
